01:42:04,458 --> 01:42:06,125
<font color="#ffff00">Aku ingin kau sembuh.</font>

1291
01:42:06,458 --> 01:42:08,583
<font color="#ffff00">Aku tak perlu penyembuhan, Yah.</font>

